noincsearch VIM Command
Explanation
noincsearch command is used to turn off incremental highlighting of the searching string while typing.
Usage:
:set noincsearch

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ex.
----
[claeyje@muscadet ~]$ cat .vimrc
syntax off
set nohlsearch
set t_Co=0
set paste
set noincsearch
filetype off
command Line :r ~/bin/line
command Date :r! date
